All right! One more time!

00:00:44.586 --> 00:00:46.546 position:50% align:center
[SASUGAI]
Nope. No more times.

00:00:53.094 --> 00:00:55.555 position:50% align:center
Tomorrow's just the fourth
competition of the series,

00:00:55.638 --> 00:00:57.349 position:50% align:center
so you've gotta
conserve your energy.

00:00:57.432 --> 00:00:58.850 position:50% align:center
[MAESHIMA]
I can't sit still.

00:00:58.933 --> 00:01:01.144 position:50% align:center
If I don't move,
I'll be like "ahh!"

00:01:01.227 --> 00:01:02.604 position:50% align:center
