00:01:02.687 --> 00:01:04.731 position:50% align:center
[SASUGAI] Channel that feeling
into the competition.

00:01:04.814 --> 00:01:08.068 position:50% align:center
Which includes resting
your body so you don't die.

00:01:08.151 --> 00:01:09.694 position:50% align:center
--I can't sleep.
--You have to.

00:01:09.778 --> 00:01:11.321 position:50% align:center
Take a warm bath,
and when you get out,

00:01:11.404 --> 00:01:12.947 position:50% align:center
use stretching and
massage to get rid of

00:01:13.031 --> 00:01:14.407 position:50% align:center
the lactic acid buildup.

00:01:14.491 --> 00:01:17.202 position:50% align:center
And eat foods high
in vitamins B1 or B2,

00:01:17.285 --> 00:01:19.037 position:50% align:center
