small for now.

00:01:19.120 --> 00:01:20.121 position:50% align:center
Also--

00:01:20.205 --> 00:01:22.540 position:50% align:center
[MAESHIMA snoring]

00:01:22.624 --> 00:01:24.042 position:50% align:center
Now you sleep...

00:01:24.125 --> 00:01:26.461 position:50% align:center
[KUBOTA]
Four toes or six toes.

00:01:26.544 --> 00:01:28.630 position:50% align:center
Selling toad oil and
it's important to know

00:01:28.713 --> 00:01:30.632 position:50% align:center
how many toes.

00:01:30.715 --> 00:01:32.634 position:50% align:center
In the front and
the back, it isn't.

00:01:32.717 --> 00:01:35.512 position:50% align:center
