so it has four blue toes.

00:01:35.595 --> 00:01:37.514 position:50% align:center
Don't forget to vacuum though.

00:01:37.597 --> 00:01:39.474 position:50% align:center
[KIRIYAMA] Schedule, check.
Map, check.

00:01:39.557 --> 00:01:42.227 position:50% align:center
Medication for Jonouchi's
motion sickness, check.

00:01:42.310 --> 00:01:44.729 position:50% align:center
Aki gets fevers, so, cooling
sheets for that, check.

00:01:47.440 --> 00:01:48.400 position:50% align:center
Oh, right.

00:01:48.483 --> 00:01:50.276 position:50% align:center
I'll need some more
pre-paid cards.

00:01:53.822 --> 00:01:55.573 position:50% align:center
[YUKIMITSU] Are you sure
you're using enough toner?

00:01:55.657 --> 00:01:56.950 position:50% align:center
[AKIMITSU]
Yeah, I think it's fine.

00:01:57.033 --> 00:01:58.410 position:50% align:center
It's important to take
care of your skin

00:01:58.493 --> 00:01:59.744 position:50% align:center
while you're still young.

00:01:59.828 --> 00:02:01.162 position:50% align:center
Good thing I don't give
a crap about stuff

00:02:01.246 --> 00:02:02.580 position:50% align:center
like that.

00:02:02.664 --> 00:02:05.875 position:50% align:center
[JONOUCHI laughing]

00:02:05.959 --> 00:02:08.169 position:50% align:center
[ELECTRONIC MOTHER]
Sota, dear? Sweetheart?

00:02:08.253 --> 00:02:10.338 position:50% align:center
How much longer will
you be playing?

00:02:10.422 --> 00:02:12.340 position:50% align:center
I couldn't sleep,
so I had no choice!

00:02:12.424 --> 00:02:13.508 position:50% align:center
[ELECTRONIC MOTHER]
My goodness!

00:02:13.591 --> 00:02:15.844 position:50% align:center
Okay, I'm going to tell
your grandmother.

00:02:26.688 --> 00:02:27.689 position:50% align:center
