Tomorrow.

00:02:31.526 --> 00:02:32.527 position:50% align:center
[KURAYOSHI gasps]

00:02:36.448 --> 00:02:38.116 position:50% align:center
So it's finally here.

00:02:38.199 --> 00:02:40.869 position:50% align:center
The day we face off directly.

00:02:40.952 --> 00:02:43.955 position:50% align:center
Hey, check it out.
The Ionodai boys, all together.

00:04:19.634 --> 00:04:21.177 position:50% align:center
[ANNOUNCER B] We're here
at the fourth competition

00:04:21.261 --> 00:04:22.846 position:50% align:center
