fourth-place winner,

00:04:40.822 --> 00:04:42.490 position:50% align:center
Ionodai High.

00:04:42.574 --> 00:04:43.742 position:50% align:center
With their carefree performance,

00:04:43.825 --> 00:04:45.660 position:50% align:center
