00:12:30.125 --> 00:12:31.501 position:50% align:center
[MICHINAGA] You can totally
see what that wild card

00:12:31.584 --> 00:12:33.169 position:50% align:center
of theirs is feeling, though.

00:12:33.253 --> 00:12:35.338 position:50% align:center
You can tell he's
desperate to win.

00:12:35.422 --> 00:12:38.800 position:50% align:center
Baring emotion can give momentum
to any performance.

00:12:38.883 --> 00:12:41.970 position:50% align:center
